bioPlain:
Dina Dillard has built her company by recognizing the current real estate sales process is flawed. Any realtor can subscribe to a MLS service and send you listings, and any potential buyer can find properties by doing their own internet search. There is no way to differentiate value when you can do the same thing as your &ldquo;realtor.&rdquo;

Dina and her team do not rely on internet search engine optimization (SEO) referrals. They believe in a collaborative approach where they will work with you to understand your personal needs. Depending on your specific preferences, they can offer transactional advice, assistance on real estate valuation , non-traditional financing, home improvement projects and provide you with competent suggestions for other professionals as part of their service commitment. She is a tenacious client representative.

Dina is locally born and raised. She grew up here, so she has witnessed the evolution of the Austin Metro real estate market. She will continue to be a fixture in the community, and she is looking forward to serving you.

Lauren is a passionate and client driven Realtor with the Spyglass Realty team. She has called Austin, Tx home for over 20 years and has experienced Austin living in most all of the city&rsquo;s neighborhoods. After spending the majority of her life and planting roots in Central Texas she knows all the amazing features and opportunities Austin and its surrounding areas have to offer and loves to share that knowledge with her clients to help them find the perfect home and neighborhood that will suit their needs. Prior to making the jump into the real estate industry, Lauren spent 15 years in the hair and makeup industry as an imaginative, adaptable, and dynamic hairstylist & make-up artist with a passion for transforming self-image & confidence. She led teams as a salon manager, worked in high pressure situations on set for photoshoots and movies, and was tenacious in securing new business & forging dedicated, loyal relationships with clients and business partners. She now brings her unwavering love for understanding and helping people to her real estate career.

&ldquo;I pride myself on my ability to truly listen and understand my clients cares and concerns, especially when it comes to making a major life decision, like home buying. Purchasing a new home can be an overwhelming or scary experience for some and my goal is to make the experience fun, and ease the mind of my clients by having open communication and showing all my clients the respect and attention they deserve!&rdquo;

Lauren is dedicated to helping you with your next real estate adventure, whether it be buying, selling, or leasing a property, she wants to help you find your personal sanctuary!
